# Motion

Motion communicates change.

Never animate for decoration alone.

---

# Principles

Fast

Purposeful

Subtle

Accessible

---

# Durations

Micro

100–150ms

Standard

200–300ms

Complex

300–500ms

Avoid long animations.

---

# Easing

Prefer Flutter Material easing.

Avoid exaggerated curves.

---

# Page Transitions

Consistent across the application.

Do not mix styles.

---

# Loading

Skeleton loaders preferred.

Avoid unnecessary spinners.

---

# Reduced Motion

Respect operating system accessibility settings.

Disable non-essential animations.

---

# Cursor Instructions

Use animation only when it improves comprehension.